Its botanical blend of lotus, gardenia and white water lily help soothe, calm, and nourish your skin.

attributes.name: Retinol
attributes.how-to-text:
* Use retinol in the evening after cleansing and toning and before other serums.
* Apply a pea sized amount to your fingers and gently tap into your skin.
attributes.description: A derivative of vitamin A that helps to promote skin renewal and enhance collagen production.
attributes.benefits: Retinol works beneath the skin surface at a cellular level to promote cell renewal and repair processes so that newer cells reach the surface quicker, resulting in brighter, smoother skin. Stimulating these renewal processes in the skin makes retinol a powerful ingredient for reversing the visible signs of ageing as well as improving overall skin clarity. A must-have for healthy skin, it aids with a number of skin concerns such as minimising the appearance of fine lines, wrinkles, uneven skin tone and hyperpigmentation.

attributes.name: Hoola Matte Bronzer
attributes.how-to-text:
* Dust onto chin, cheeks and forehead to sculpt and define.
* Starting under cheekbones, use circular motions to blend upwards onto the cheeks.

* Buff along the temple and top of the forehead for even radiance.

attributes.name: Colorful Vitamin Face Mask
attributes.how-to-text:
1. Unfold the mask.
2. Apply mask to clean, dry skin.
3. Leave for 5 minutes.
4. Remove mask and gently massage in any remaining product. No need to rinse.

Frequency of use: Twice weekly.

Papaya: Known for its high vitamin content and radiance-boosting effect.
Mango: Known for its sugar, protein and amino-acid content. Boasts perfect moisturizing properties to nourish the skin.
Aloe vera: Saturated with water and known for its sugar content. Moisturizes the skin and protects it from dehydration.
Dragon fruit: Known for its high vitamin content and skin-purifying effect.

attributes.name: Retract Waterproof Eyeliner
attributes.how-to-text:
* With a steady hand, draw the eyeliner along your upper lash line, as close to your lashes as possible, beginning at the inner corner of your eye.
* Draw a thin line in the same direction on your lower lash line, starting from the middle of the lash line this time.
* Do not stretch your skin too much, as it can make the look messy and uneven.
attributes.description: A precise waterproof retractable eyeliner pencil with a tip for blending and an integrated sharpener.
attributes.benefits: A waterproof retractable eyeliner that accurately lines the eye contour with intense color. Its creamy texture allows the tip to glide along the eye contour, while the tip blends the line for a smoky effect.

* Draw a thin line in the same direction on your lower lash line, starting from the middle of the lash line this time.
* Use the smudge-tip to perfect your lines. 
* Do not stretch your skin too much, as it can make the look messy and uneven.
